=== Line Chart Widget ===

{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.DisplayConfigurationWidget
| clazz = com.fluidops.iwb.widget.LineChartWidget
| type = 'DESCRIPTION'
}}
Go back to [[Help:Widgets | Widgets ]]

==== Configuration Settings ====

{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.DisplayConfigurationWidget
| clazz = com.fluidops.iwb.widget.LineChartWidget
}}

==== Examples ====
===== Simple =====
<source>
{{#widget: LineChart | 
 input = 'Org'
 | query = '
    SELECT ?Org ?projects WHERE { 
        VALUES (?Org ?projects)
        { 
          ("Org 1" 23)
          ("Org 2" 56)
          ("Org 3" 33)
          ("Org 4" 87)
          ("Org 5" 20)
          ("Org 6" 15)
          ("Org 7" 90)
          ("Org 8" 55)
          ("Org 9" 6)
   } }'
 | output = {{ 'projects' }}
 | styling = 
   {{ height = '300'
    | width = '600'
   }}
}}
</source>

{{#widget: LineChart | 
 input = 'Org'
 | query = '
